# MQTT topic ACL — Omni-Sense
# Each sensor may only publish to its own subtopic.
# The gateway service may subscribe to all sensor topics.

# Gateway service — full read access
user gateway
topic read omni/#

# Pattern ACL: sensors can only publish to their own sensor_id path
# %u = MQTT username (which equals the cert CN = sensor_id)
pattern write omni/sensor/+/%u/acoustic
pattern write omni/sensor/+/%u/telemetry

# No sensor may subscribe to anything (publish-only devices)
